'''野百合'''（{{sn|''Lilium brownii''}}）也叫'''淡紫百合'''，是[[百合科|百合科]][[百合属|百合属]][[多年生草本植物|多年生草本植物]]，原产[[甘肃|甘肃]]、[[陕西|陕西]]、[[山西|山西]]、[[河北|河北]]、[[河南|河南]]、[[安徽|安徽]]、[[江苏|江苏]]、[[浙江|浙江]]、[[江西|江西]]、[[湖南|湖南]]、[[湖北|湖北]]、[[重庆|重庆]]、[[四川|四川]]、[[贵州|贵州]]、[[云南|云南]]、[[广西|广西]]、[[广东|广东]]、[[香港|香港]]、[[福建|福建]]、[[金门|金门]]、[[马祖|马祖]]<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=''Lilium brownii''|url=http://www.efloras.org/florataxon.aspx?flora_id=2&taxon_id=200027704|accessdate=2020-01-13|author=|date=|format=|work=Flora of China|publisher=efloras.org|language=|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917225622/http://www.efloras.org/florataxon.aspx?flora_id=2&taxon_id=200027704|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=野百合|url=http://www.producegreen.org.hk/hkwildflower/100flower/flower_113.htm|accessdate=2020-01-14|author=|date=|format=|work=香港野花網|publisher=綠田園基金|language=|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917151408/http://www.producegreen.org.hk/hkwildflower/100flower/flower_113.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=利用RAPD及rDNA ITS分子標誌分析馬祖原生百合遺傳歧異度|author=簡婉婷|url=http://www.airitilibrary.com/Publication/alDetailedMesh1?DocID=U0001-1608201010345700|journal=學位論文|publisher=臺灣大學園藝學研究所|issue=|doi=10.6342/ntu.2010.01634|others=|year=2010|volume=|page=|language=|pmid=|access-date=2020-01-14|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920013754/https://www.airitilibrary.com/Publication/alDetailedMesh1?DocID=U0001-1608201010345700|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及[[越南|越南]]中北部<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Averyanov|first=Leonid V.|last2=Tanaka|first2=Noriyuki|last3=Nguyen|first3=Khang Sinh|date=2016|title=New Species - ''Lilium procumbens'' and its Allies in the Flora of Vietnam|url=http://www.airitilibrary.com/Publication/alDetailedMesh?DocID=0372333X-201603-201603150001-201603150001-1-7|journal=Taiwania|language=zh|volume=61|issue=1|pages=1–7|doi=10.6165/tai.2016.61.1|issn=0372-333X|via=|access-date=2020-05-31|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919213412/https://www.airitilibrary.com/Publication/alDetailedMesh?DocID=0372333X-201603-201603150001-201603150001-1-7|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[缅甸|缅甸]][[克钦邦|克钦邦]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Kress|first=W. John|last2=DeFilipps|first2=Robert A.|last3=Farr|first3=Ellen|last4=Kyi|first4=Daw Yin Yin|date=2003|title=A Checklist of the Trees, Shrubs, Herbs, and Climbers of Myanmar (Revised from the original works by J. H. Lace, R. Rodger, H. G. Hundley, and U Chit Ko Ko on the "List of Trees, Shrubs, Herbs and Principal Climbers, etc. Recorded from Burma")|journal=Contributions from the United States National Herbarium|volume=45|pages=1–590|jstor=23493222|issn=0097-1618}}</ref>。

种名''brownii''以苏格兰植物学家Robert Brown（1773-1858）的名字命名。

==亚种==
[[File:Lilium_japonicum_2_(lit).jpg|缩略图]] {{lang|la|''Lilium brownii'' var. ''viridulum''}}]]
野百合种下有两个变种<ref name=":0" />：
*'''野百合''' {{lang|la|''Lilium brownii'' var. ''brownii''}}：叶披针形至条形。
*[[百合_(植物)|百合]] {{lang|la|''Lilium brownii'' var. ''viridulum'' Baker}}：叶倒披针形至倒卵形。

